    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/Styles/footer.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>
    <section class="hero-section">
      <div class="hero-bg"></div>
      <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="display-4">Learning Hooman</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
          Online Tutoring services for Maths, Science & ELA | Middle School,
          High School and College level
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Enroll Today</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      <h1>
        LEARNING HOOMAN IS A REVOLUTIONARY ONLINE LEARNING PLATFORM WITH A
        MISSION TO PROVIDE ACADEMIC EXCELLENCE
      </h1>
      <p>
        At Learning Hooman, we understand that traditional classrooms can't
        always offer the personalized attention every student deserves. That's
        why we've designed an exceptional online tutoring experience, focusing
        on one-on-one sessions that adapt to your child's unique pace and your
        family's schedule.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our mission is to make learning enjoyable and effective. We achieve this
        by connecting students with our team of knowledgeable and dependable
        educators. These aren't just teachers; they're mentors dedicated to
        strengthening concepts, boosting enthusiasm, and fostering your child's
        growth in an ever-evolving learning landscape. We also incorporate
        methods designed to *train the brain and increase brain power*, helping
        students unlock their full potential. We carefully match each student
        with a highly qualified tutor to ensure the best possible personalized
        learning journey.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our knowledgeable teachers have years of expertise in education. They
        are mentors who care about your child’s growth and development. Each
        student is carefully matched with a tutor by our custom, highly
        qualified teaching staff for the best one-on-one learning experience.
      </p>
      <a href="/about" class="learn-more-btn">LEARN MORE</a>
    </section>

    <div class="student-section">
      <section class="section-container">
        <div class="image-column">
          <!-- Replace 'path/to/your/image.jpg' with the actual path to your image -->
          <img
            src="/Images/Student-profile-pic.png"
            alt="Student receiving personalized instruction"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="content-column">
          <h2>Personalized instruction for each student</h2>
          <p>
            Our tutors are accessible during a range of time frames. The
            tutoring schedule is specifically created to accommodate each
            student's unique pace. Not only is our learning strategy adjustable
            for your child, we strictly adhere to the academic timetable
            established by your school, give extra attention to your specific
            needs and design lessons around your schedule.
          </p>
          <p>
            We offer individualized, cost-efficient, and successful online
            tutoring services. You can also take advantage of our online
            practice exams and exercises for better academic outcomes or receive
            immediate assistance with your homework.
          </p>
          <p>
            You can be confident that your child will receive the greatest
            education possible under the direction of our knowledgeable and
            experienced tutors. Our online tutoring services are here to boost
            your child's self-assurance, independence, and academic achievement
            while alleviating your stress and worries about offering the best
            possible academic help.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our individualized, encouraging, and compassionate online teaching
            staff ensures the outcomes you and your child deserve.
          </p>
          <p>
            We take each student's academic performance very seriously! So
            schedule a free consultation with us!
          </p>
          <div class="button-group">
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">EXPLORE TUTORING</a>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">SCHEDULE A FREE SESSION</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div
      class="container-fluid d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center min-vh-50 p-4 features-section"
    >
      <div class="container-xl">
        <!-- Section Title -->
        <h2 class="display-4 fw-bold text-center mb-5 pb-4">
          Why Families Love Us
        </h2>

        <!-- Features Grid Container -->
        <div class="row g-4 g-lg-5 justify-content-center">
          <!-- Feature 1: Test Prep Tutoring -->
          <div class="col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-2">
