                      </li>
                       <li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3">
                          <svg class="check-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                          <span class="fs-5 text-secondary">Adjustable schedules</span>
                      </li>
                       <li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3">
                          <svg class="check-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                          <span class="fs-5 text-secondary">Expert tutors for middle, high school, and graduation levels.</span>
                      </li>
                       <li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3">
                          <svg class="check-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                          <span class="fs-5 text-secondary">Personalised one-on-one live tutoring</span>
                      </li>
                       <li class="d-flex align-items-start mb-3">
                          <svg class="check-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                          <span class="fs-5 text-secondary">Assistance with homework and timely syllabus completion.</span>
                      </li>
                       <li class="d-flex align-items-start">
                          <svg class="check-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
